{
  "texts": [
    "Currently, there is a paucity of surveys on the use of retrieval augmentation to enhance the performance of LLMs.",
    "Zhao et al. (2023) provide a comprehensive overview of work on RAG for multimodality.",
    "Zhao et al. (2024a) concentrate on the utilisation of retrieval augmentation generation techniques for the Artificial Intelligence Generated Content (AIGC) domain.",
    "This article provides a comprehensive overview of recent RAG work, but it does not cover all relevant domains.",
    "Additionally, the article lacks sufficient detail to provide a comprehensive timeline of the overall development."
  ]
}